{"tid":1590284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣］［制裁通緝令］香港人權與民主法案 制裁名單","createTime":"2019-09-23T15:53:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T06:16:15.000Z","uid":217430,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d13c9e95eb83a972556c455fe0bbc4fcb20080a9","tid":1590284,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:53:33.000Z","msg":"法案好快就會通過，我地好應該整一set關於<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">制裁名單既文宣</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得可以用<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">制裁通緝令</span></span></span>既形式。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SPVvd3k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSPVvd3k.jpg&h=80beee43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相中有將會被制裁人士既大頭相，下面有佢既賣港罪名。<br />\n<br />\n人士眾多，為左方便香港人入腦。制裁通緝令既邊框可以做個顏色分類。<br />\n<br />\n比如<br />\n<br />\n紅色：<span style=\"color: red;\">親中人士</span><br />\n藍色：<span style=\"color: blue;\">警犬</span><br />\n...等等<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連儂牆直頭可以整個<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">通緝令專區</span></span>，上面貼住一張張制裁通緝令。<br />\n<br />\n不定期更新，保持法案議題既熱度之餘，又可以比大家對住張相屌下，旁邊加多隻拖鞋打下小人又得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n甚至可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">痴係地下</span></span>，來個密集攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tch5Nvg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTch5Nvg.jpg&h=76a79f88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab1416552a27bab96adfc7151ca65cd566670aa","tid":1590284,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"39e5625cd96f0acc477cba2ef0d0cdfa7c0c988f","tid":1590284,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:54:53.000Z","msg":"我係召集今日喺始創唱國歌嗰個小薯仔，我有啲嘢想講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"931b4916813d6c07dfc798db13647f3c1928d0c8","tid":1590284,"uid":136992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:54:58.000Z","msg":"[航拍J召喚]十月一國旗維港上空飄揚<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590267\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590267</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n成個維港上空都係美國旗一定激死支共"},{"pid":"1b483c206779550c9ba49eb19670ea036c1e01a6","tid":1590284,"uid":75385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:56:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00671d8218634b74e2ec8d7b3004cfda4ab2d838","tid":1590284,"uid":268217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:56:29.000Z","msg":"good idea!"},{"pid":"c31b505fb73d4070f468db82022d055e10f2c1e2","tid":1590284,"uid":268217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:57:49.000Z","msg":"最好有埋片!<br />\n有冇人一直做緊呢件事？<br />\n<br />\n可以搞最出位個啲先？"},{"pid":"333577cad510b1ced778afcaa890350562eecbd5","tid":1590284,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c31b505fb73d4070f468db82022d055e10f2c1e2","tid":1590284,"uid":268217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:57:49.000Z","msg":"最好有埋片!<br />\n有冇人一直做緊呢件事？<br />\n<br />\n可以搞最出位個啲先？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:00:57.000Z","msg":"整位個qr code （入面係片）係罪行個度"},{"pid":"289ac60a20fbb23a76e